042021             0059*   @end:
042021             0060*   
042021             0061*   ; VDU 23, 27, 6, n: Add bitmap n as a frame to current sprite (where bitmap's buffer ID is 64000+n)
042021             0062*   ; inputs: a is the 8-bit bitmap number
042021             0063*   ; prerequisites: vdu_sprite_select
